complicated to reproduce than I'd expected, it's not impossible.  I can't
see reproducing the shorter stem, though, if the better one is available.

I'm also thinking of maybe adding a channel through the ball on the stem, up
through the stem for possibly wiring something (alarm LED?) inside of the
mirror.  Not that I'm exactly sure how to get the wires from the sending
device, up to the mirror mounting point on the roof...

> > ... noticed that the collar that accepts the ball seems
> > to be deteriorating...
> This is pretty common and Id be glad to listen to suggestions on this
