The cup is the top of the glare adjusting mech.  Replacing it means
replacing the main part of the mech.  My mirror housing is severely sun
damaged.  Repair will probably replace the texturing on the back of the
housing with a different surface, but replacing the glare mech will
definitely take care of the deteriorated cup.  Not sure what to replace the
little friction disk in the cup with, so I'm saving mine for the new
housing.

